<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ku Zo Mu Bi Mai Ceto LW456</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ku zo mu bi Mai Ceto
 Ko da shi ke duniya na kiranku,
 Shi ne ya bada ransa
 Don ya cece mu ya ba mu sabon rai
 Wata rana za mu je
 Ku zamna wurinsa
 Ya kamata dai mu yi aniya cikin aikinsa
 Ku zo mu bi Mai Ceto
 Sa'anan mu yi murna har abada.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>456</hymn_number>
</song>